Business Brief -- American Telephone  Telegraph:
   Sales, Service Group Formed
   For Video Communications
ATT said it formed dedicated sales and service teams,
called Global Business Video Services and Global Business
Video Systems, to provide customers with end-to-end video
applications, including connections to its PBX systems and
world-wide communications network, as well as video systems
and a full range of design, installation and maintenance
options for equipment and services. The company is based in
Basking Ridge, N.J.